    <thetext>I was just playing around with 2.10 rc1 for testing. I opened a map and wanted to know what would happen if I tried to add a different maps module in parallel view. However, Bibletime offers me maps in addition to DICTIONARY modules to pick from. I can open those alongside the maps module, but all that will be shown is the selected entry in the dictionary. 

Steps to reproduce: 
1. open a maps module
2. click on the button to add a parallel work
3. In the list of offered modules, look for dictionary as well as maps modules. 

This is on Sword 1.7.0.</thetext>
